title: Statement by the Press Secretary on the Visit of NATO Secretary-General Rasmussen | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
May 07, 2012

 



Statement by the Press Secretary on the Visit of NATO Secretary-General Rasmussen





	The President will host NATO Secretary-General Rasmussen for a meeting in the Oval Office on May 9.Â  The two leaders will discuss final preparations for the NATO Summit the President will host in Chicago on May 20-21.
